SUMMARY:GTApreneurs March 31-2026 Business Networking Event Vaughan - Toro
 nto
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\nJoin us at 
 an exciting Business Networking Event in Vaughan (1 block north of Toronto
 ) on Tuesday March 31 where you can meet potential clients and referral pa
 rtners\, learn something new\, enjoy a meal and promote your business!\n\n
 This event will feature our President of GTApreneurs\, **Tammy Defoe**\, w
 ho excels at helping entrepreneurs get more exposure and more clients. She
  is a Business Coach and Consultant specializing in business development\,
  sales\, marketing\, digital marketing\, public speaking\, business commun
 ication and networking.\n\n**REGISTER HERE:** https://gtapreneurs.com/netw
 orking-events-vaughan\n\n**VENUE:** Improve Canada\, 2nd floor auditorium\
 n**ADDRESS:** 7250 Keele St\, Vaughan\, ON (Between Steeles Ave W. and 407
 )\n\n**PARKING:** Free\, onsite. Park on the NORTH SIDE of the building of
 f of Snidercroft Rd\n\n**\\*\\*DIRECTIONS TO FIND THE ROOM:** Walk through
  entrance M\, go straight ahead until you get to the main aisle. Straight 
 ahead will be a staircase. If you prefer to take the elevator\, make a rig
 ht at the main aisle\, go down a few stores and you will see it on the lef
 t.\n\n**EVENT ITINERARY:**\n\n* **5:00-6:00pm:** Open networking\, food bu
 ffet\, visit exhibitor booths\n* **6:00-6:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming pr
 esentation\n* **6:10-6:30pm:** Guest Speaker Presentation\n* **6:30-7:00pm
 :** Exhibitor Introductions + member Elevator Pitches\n* **7:00-8:00pm:** 
 Open networking\, visit exhibitor booths\n\n**MENU:** Pizza\, Veggies\, Fr
 uit\, dessert and other snacks\n**BEVERAGES:** Pop and water\n\n**TICKETS*
 *\n\n* **GTApreneurs' Referral Group\, Exhibitor and Mega Networking Membe
 rs:** Free\n* **Non-members:** $27 in advance or $29 on event day\n\n***No
 t a GTApreneurs Member?*** Go here to view our memberships and register: h
 ttps://gtapreneurs.com/business-networking-memberships\n\n**QUESTIONS ABOU
 T THE EVENT?**\n\nCall or text Tammy at (416) 522-7770 or info@gtapreneurs
 .com.\n\nTo learn about Tammy Defoe's business coaching services\, please 
 go to https://gtapreneurs.com/about and https://gtapreneurs.com/business-c
 oaching-toronto\n\n**EXHIBITORS:**\n\n* **Gorette Marques\,** Realty Execu
 tive Plus\, https://gmarquesrealtor.com\n* **Sonia Kurmey\,** Arbonne\, ww
 w.soniakurmey.arbonne.com\n* **Balbir Pabila\,** PPLSI\\~LegalShield\, htt
 ps://bkpabila.legalshieldassociate.com\n* **Abhishek Basak\,** Clerk Tech\
 , www.clerk-tech.com\n* **Monica Hecht\,** The Village Hive\, www.thevilla
 gehive.ca\n* **Ian McIntosh\,** DigiMinds Bots \\| Exhibitor Follow Up Pro
 \\\, [www.digimindscrm.com](www.digimindscrm.com)\n* **Brad Aylward\,** BH
 A Mortgage Corp. Mortgage Architects LIC # 12728\, www.bhamortgagecorp.com
 \n* **Adrian Newman\,** Numero Uno Web Solutions Inc.\, www.numerounoweb.c
 om\n* **Sehej Arora\,** Mani Law Group\, www.manilaw.ca\n\n\\*Exhibitor ta
 bles available. Visit www.gtapreneurs.com/exhibitor to book a spot\n\n\\*W
 e will EMAIL you the GUEST CONTACT SHEET the day after the event by 5pm. I
 f you don't receive it in your inbox\, please check your SPAM/JUNK folder.
  Note: You must attend the event to receive the guest contact sheet.
